OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776985387
OL,3,CFire crews called to Kent marshes to
OL,4,Ctackle grassland blaze
OL,6,FFire crews have been tackling a blaze
OL,7,Fin Swanscombe, Kent after a large area
OL,8,Fof grassland caught alight.
OL,10,FSix fire engines and an all-terrain
OL,11,Fvehicle were called to the scene at
OL,12,FSwanscombe Marshes on Thursday evening
OL,13,F(23 April) where around five hectares
OL,14,Fof grassland were alight.
OL,16,FCrews say they have made good progress
OL,17,Fand have been damping down hot spots.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
