OL,3,CFire crews called to Kent marshes to
OL,4,Ctackle grassland blaze
OL,6,FPeople living in the area and
OL,7,Fneighbouring Greenhithe were advised
OL,8,Fto keep windows and doors closed to
OL,9,Favoid smoke inhalation. This warning
OL,10,Fhas now been lifted and there have
OL,11,Fbeen no reported injuries.
OL,13,FKent Fire and Rescue Service have
OL,14,Fasked the public to share information
OL,15,Fwith any loved ones in the affected
OL,16,Farea who may not have access to the
OL,17,Finternet.
